descriptionNullable:
### Context

During this pandemic , let us explore about different infectious diseases which we came across in entire world from 2001 to 2014


### Content

**About Dataset**

- Disease    :  Name of the Disease (disease type)
- country    :  Name of the Country
- year          : happened in which year
- Sex           : type of gender
- Count       : no of people effected
- Population : population of a country at particular year
- Rate            : most happening rate
- CI.lower      : lower Class Interval  (The confidence interval [CI] is a range of values that's likely to include a population 
                          value with a certain degree of confidence.)
- CI.upper      : upper Class Interval  (The confidence interval [CI] is a range of values that's likely to include a 
                          population value with a certain degree of confidence.)


### Acknowledgements

This Data was officially given by Data.world
title: Infectious Disease Cases Data
subtitle: Worldwide Infectious Disease cases from 2001-2014
